'''Confetti Shark''' is a {{Rarity|Limited}} fish found in special pools in the [[Ocean]] during the [[Golden Tide]] event.

== Description ==
{{Description|A festive predator that appears during the Golden Tide celebration, known for its colorful scales that seem to shimmer and shed like confetti in the water. These sharks are drawn to the excitement of celebration, making them a sought-after catch during festivities.|Bestiary Entry}}

